OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain will soon clear east then
OL,6,Fsunny spells and showers. Drier for a
OL,7,Ftime in the afternoon before further
OL,8,Fshowers later, heavy at times. Cool
OL,9,Fand blustery.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClear spells and variable
OL,12,Fcloud in the evening with a few
OL,13,Fshowers in places. Largely dry but
OL,14,Fcloudy overnight with a few showers
OL,15,Fagain towards morning. Patchy frost in
OL,16,Fplaces.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool with
OL,19,Fbright or sunny spells and scattered
OL,20,Fheavy showers. Chance of overnight
OL,21,Ffrost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
